IWLCA Acknowledges 2024 Division I All-American Teams

48 student-athletes honored

 

NORTHBOROUGH, MASS. – The IWLCA has named the 48 student-athletes who were selected for one of the 2024 Division I All-American teams – honorees are divided into first, second, and third teams. This group of IWLCA All-Americans represent 21 different institutions and are the best athletes in our game this year.
